      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <table frame="all"
                rowsep="1"
                colsep="1"
                id="table_h1v_4w2_lcc"
                class="- topic/table ">
            <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup ">
               <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="1*" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="danger" id="note_vp2_pw2_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Danger of electric shock! </b>Contact  with live components pose a
                              risk of serious injury or even death!<ul id="ul_kn2_vw2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Before starting work, switch off the electric power supply.
                                    Follow plant requirements for lockout tagout.  </li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note type="danger" id="note_u54_rw2_lcc" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Life threatening hazard due to a falling vertical carriage! </b>
                              The unsecured vertical carriage can fall down  and cause serious
                              injury or even death! <ul id="ul_q2r_5w2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Always make sure that the safety bolts of the vertical carriage
                                    are properly installed before carrying out work on / near the
                                    carriage! </li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note id="note_j2x_vw2_lcc" type="warning" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Dangerof injury from improperly performed maintenance! </b>Improper
                              maintenance canresult in serious personal injury or material
                              damage!</p>
                           <ul id="ul_jmx_51f_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Before starting work, ensure that you have sufficient space!</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Handle open, sharp-edged components with care!</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Pay attention to cleanliness and orderliness at the place of work!
                                 Loose components and tools lying around are a potential cause of
                                 accidents!</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Install all components correctly. Observe the prescribed bolt
                                 tightening torques! Secure the bolts with bolt locking com- pound
                                 (e.g. Weicon AN 302-43 (blue)) “medium strength”!</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Secure components so that they cannot fall down or fall over!</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Operating elements of the Emergency Stop system must be freely
                                 accessible!</li>
                              <li class="- topic/li ">Operate the machine only when all the safety devices, e.g. safety
                                 fence, light barriers and safety bolts are installed and fully
                                 functional! </li>
                           </ul>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note id="note_ytk_zw2_lcc" type="warning" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Risk of injury from stored pneumatic energy! </b>Pneumatic energy
                              may be stored in the machine that can lead to uncontrolled movements
                              of components and injuries!<ul id="ul_jsm_bx2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Follow plant requirements for lockout tagout of the system.
                                    Only thenstart the maintenance work!</li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note id="note_e2n_zw2_lcc" type="warning" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Dangerof crushing! </b> There are several crushing points on the
                              machine that can cause injuries!<ul id="ul_h1k_cx2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Do not reach between the following points: <ul id="ul_pny_cx2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                       <li class="- topic/li ">the vertical carriage and the steel housing</li>
                                       <li class="- topic/li ">the vertical carriage and the lifting mast</li>
                                       <li class="- topic/li ">the locking pins and the container</li>
                                       <li class="- topic/li ">the vertical carriage and the horizontal carriage!</li>
                                    </ul>
                                 </li>
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">No person is allowed inside the safety fence area when the
                                    machine is switched on!</li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note id="note_wpp_zw2_lcc" type="warning" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Danger due to non-observance of the prohibition of transporting
                                 persons!</b> The MSK transfer system can pose a serious risk in the
                              event ofnon-compliance and/or circumvention of the prohibition of
                              trans- porting persons.</p>
                        </note>
                        <ul id="ul_t2f_3bf_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                           <li class="- topic/li ">Only operate the transfer system when all safety devices are in place
                              and in proper working condition, such as the programmed safety
                              interlocks and physical E-Stops. </li>
                           <li class="- topic/li "> Nopersons are allowed on the transfer system!</li>
                        </ul>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note id="note_e3w_gx2_lcc" type="warning" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Risk of injury due to stored hydraulic energy! </b> Hydraulic
                              energy can be stored in the machine and cause the un- controlled
                              movement of components, which can lead to severe in- juries!<ul id="ul_kxc_kx2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Switch off the MSK system, as explained in this document.</li>
                                 <li class="- topic/li "> Do not begin maintenance work until then!</li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note id="note_xd2_hx2_lcc" type="warning" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Risk of injury due to laser radiation! </b>Laser radiation can
                              cause serious eye damage.<ul id="ul_akt_lx2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Do not look into the laser beam!</li>
                                 <li class="- topic/li "> If it is not possible to avoid looking directly into the laser
                                    beam (e.g., during maintenance work), suitable eye protection
                                    must be worn.</li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry "/>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <note id="note_qp5_hx2_lcc" type="caution" class="- topic/note ">
                           <p class="- topic/p ">
                              <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Dangerof electric shock!</b> Parts of the machine may still be live
                              even when the emergency stop switch has been pressed!<ul id="ul_tmk_nx2_lcc" class="- topic/ul ">
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Do not touch live parts and leads!</li>
                                 <li class="- topic/li ">Observe the instructions in the operating manual!</li>
                              </ul>
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
